━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Nothing in this repository constitutes investment advice. The strategy
parameters (position sizing, stop-loss, trailing thresholds, indicator
thresholds, etc.) present in the source code reflect one particular
live-traded configuration of one particular instrument during one particular
market regime. Do not fork these numbers verbatim. Backtest. Paper trade.
Read the retraction essay at https://www.ibitlabs.com/essays about why
narrow-window backtests lie. Trade your own money with your own judgment.
